{
  "stem": "10353.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were put into a-- into a factory that was producing cases for anti-aircraft shells.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, that was the duty of the-- of the brigade.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But by that time, Budapest was bombed constantly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was bombed constantly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we endured some horrific, horrific bombardment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In that area where we were, that was a factory area, a highly industrialized area.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was being targeted right along.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I remember one Sunday morning, we were so heavily bombarded.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And being in a factory that made those cases, there was a lot of lumber.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so the lumber was piled up real high in the whole-- in the backyard.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And for [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] shelter, for air-raid shelters, they dug trenches underneath those piles of lumber.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And whenever there was a-- the sirens were go on, we would have to run into those trenches to hide.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that particular Sunday morning-- and I believe it was very close to Rosh Hashanah, or maybe the day before Rosh Hashanah-- we received a bombardment from 8:30 in the morning till 2:30 in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And at one point, there was one bomb that fell about 20 meters from us and it created a tremendous crater.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We thought that we were all dead, but luckily, we were safe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Allied bombs, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, the bombing was so heavy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Budapest got it really strong because the Americans would-- would bomb during the day, and the British would bomb during the night.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This was OK.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This was the way life was going on until September the 15th.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on September the 15, the Hungarian government tried to capitulate.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
